  \ wasted then i plan to do a road trip alone on my bike amritsar to goa i was 2310km\
  \ i get two and a half day to get there it was so awsome i met lot of new people\
  \ round that trip and make so my friends do some awsome things i am passionate about\
  \ nature i love clicking pics and i am very good at that on that i use to know that\
  \ i am good photographer one more thing that i get know about my self is that i\
  \ dance and sing too it was life changing exprince for me after i go on two more\
  \ road trips and  now i am in italy"
